commit.message: Updating for 0.7.2
Commenting
Add config for user profile.
Gem bumping.
Revert change meant to help in multi-user environments.
Add performance note.
Flip RbConfig conditional around the correct direction. (Config currently still resolves in 1.9 w/ a warning)
Fix typo screwing up path finding.
Fix method that wasn't moved from class to instance.
Fix path to test_helper for ruby1.9
Directly shell to libreoffice if available, otherwise fallback to JODConverter.
Add an office_path and raise OfficeNotFound if an office lib can't be found.
Rename PdfExtractor#extract_pdfs to #extract
Move methods from class methods to instance methods.
Add a PdfExtractor class to replace JODConverter.
Preparing for 0.7.0
Adding Docsplit.extract_info to close out #46
Fixing normalize_value.
ensure_pdfs now uses a new tmpdir each time it's called.
Fix ruby1.8 compatibility in info extractor.
